com.paymill.models

Class Subscription

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paymill.models.Subscription

  • public final class Subscription
extends Object
    Subscriptions allow you to charge recurring payments on a client’s credit card / to a client’s direct debit. A subscription connects a client to the Offers. A client can have several subscriptions to different offers, but only one subscription to the same offer.
    Since:
    3.0.0
    Author:
    Vassil Nikolov
